      • prepareNeededFiles

        private void prepareNeededFiles()
        Prepares the files some tests may need. It will copy some backups files (sc_points.backup.json and sc_config.backup.json) to good files (sc_points.json ans sc_config.json) after having deleted the previous versions of these files. So the tests which need to check some on-going-notifications can work because the standalone mode will have the very files it needs.
